{
  "texts": [
    "Importantly, changes made in the Opinion Region are seamlessly integrated by AI and reflected in ongoing discussions, and Ask for JustificationAI selects the dimension with the largest difference and asks people \"why\".",
    "Give JustificationHuman gives justification or questions/challenges the AI.",
    "Respond CriticallyAI responds with respect and critical thoughts (if the justification is datarelated, reply with DS-model's knowledge).",
    "Update Opinions?-Update -Keep -Tell/Ask AI more AI Opinion UpdateAI briefly summarizes what has been discussed and makes updates on the discussed dimensions.",
    "Summarize Similarities and DifferencesAI summarizes agreements, and ranks disagreements."
  ]
}